{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":958,"text":"So when I was in Morocco,"},{"time":3158,"text":"in Casablanca, not so long ago,"},{"time":5692,"text":"I met a young unmarried mother called Faiza."},{"time":10168,"text":"Faiza showed me photos of her infant son"},{"time":13505,"text":"and she told me the story of his conception,\npregnancy, and delivery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19640,"text":"It was a remarkable tale,"},{"time":21600,"text":"but Faiza saved the best for last."},{"time":25280,"text":"\"You know, I am a virgin,\" she told me."},{"time":28850,"text":"\"I have two medical certificates to prove it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":33254,"text":"This is the modern Middle East,"},{"time":35878,"text":"where two millennia after the coming of Christ,"},{"time":38510,"text":"virgin births are still a fact of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42738,"text":"Faiza's story is just one of hundreds I've heard \nover the years, traveling across the Arab region"},{"time":48395,"text":"talking to people about sex."},{"time":51683,"text":"Now, I know this might sound like a dream job,"},{"time":54899,"text":"or possibly a highly dubious occupation,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58167,"text":"but for me, it's something else altogether."},{"time":61523,"text":"I'm half Egyptian, and I'm Muslim."},{"time":64111,"text":"But I grew up in Canada, far from my Arab roots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67902,"text":"Like so many who straddle East and West,"},{"time":70536,"text":"I've been drawn, over the years, to try to better\nunderstand my origins."},{"time":75459,"text":"That I chose to look at sex comes from \nmy background in HIV/AIDS,"},{"time":79579,"text":"as a writer and a researcher and an activist."},{"time":83666,"text":"Sex lies at the heart of an emerging epidemic\nin the Middle East and North Africa,"},{"time":88790,"text":"which is one of only two regions in the world\nwhere HIV/AIDS is still on the rise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95335,"text":"Now sexuality is an incredibly powerful lens"},{"time":98376,"text":"with which to study any society,"},{"time":101100,"text":"because what happens in our intimate lives"},{"time":103609,"text":"is reflected by forces on a bigger stage:"},{"time":107783,"text":"in politics and economics, in religion and tradition, \nin gender and generations."},{"time":113857,"text":"As I found, if you really want to know a people,"},{"time":117144,"text":"you start by looking inside their bedrooms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121668,"text":"Now to be sure, the Arab world is vast and varied."},{"time":125860,"text":"But running across it are three red lines --"},{"time":128521,"text":"these are topics you are not supposed \nto challenge in word or deed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133735,"text":"The first of these is politics."},{"time":136150,"text":"But the Arab Spring has changed all that,"},{"time":138578,"text":"in uprisings which have blossomed \nacross the region since 2011."},{"time":143600,"text":"Now while those in power, old and new,"},{"time":146461,"text":"continue to cling to business as usual,"},{"time":149263,"text":"millions are still pushing back,"},{"time":151869,"text":"and pushing forward to what they hope\nwill be a better life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156984,"text":"That second red line is religion."},{"time":160164,"text":"But now religion and politics are connected,"},{"time":162995,"text":"with the rise of such groups as the \nMuslim Brotherhood."},{"time":166139,"text":"And some people, at least, are starting \nto ask questions"},{"time":169599,"text":"about the role of Islam in public and private life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174667,"text":"You know, as for that third red line, \nthat off-limits subject,"},{"time":178418,"text":"what do you think it might be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180196,"text":"Audience: Sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181258,"text":"Shereen El Feki: Louder, I can't hear you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182558,"text":"Audience: Sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183414,"text":"SEF: Again, please don't be shy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185036,"text":"Audience: Sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186088,"text":"SEF: Absolutely, that's right, it's sex. (Laughter)"},{"time":193145,"text":"Across the Arab region, the only accepted\ncontext for sex is marriage --"},{"time":199353,"text":"approved by your parents, sanctioned by religion"},{"time":203131,"text":"and registered by the state."},{"time":205671,"text":"Marriage is your ticket to adulthood."},{"time":208554,"text":"If you don't tie the knot, you can't \nmove out of your parents' place,"},{"time":212379,"text":"and you're not supposed to be having sex,"},{"time":214680,"text":"and you're definitely not supposed \nto be having children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217827,"text":"It's a social citadel; it's an impregnable fortress"},{"time":221193,"text":"which resists any assault, any alternative."},{"time":225658,"text":"And around the fortress is this vast field of taboo"},{"time":229666,"text":"against premarital sex, against condoms,"},{"time":234639,"text":"against abortion, against homosexuality,"},{"time":237583,"text":"you name it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239754,"text":"Faiza was living proof of this."},{"time":242978,"text":"Her virginity statement was \nnot a piece of wishful thinking."},{"time":247259,"text":"Although the major religions of the region\nextoll premarital chastity,"},{"time":252582,"text":"in a patriarchy, boys will be boys."},{"time":255886,"text":"Men have sex before marriage,"},{"time":257839,"text":"and people more or less turn a blind eye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261629,"text":"Not so for women,"},{"time":263845,"text":"who are expected to be virgins \non their wedding night --"},{"time":266889,"text":"that is, to turn up with your hymen intact."},{"time":271139,"text":"This is not a question of individual concern,"},{"time":274814,"text":"this is a matter of family honor, \nand in particular, men's honor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279956,"text":"And so women and their relatives"},{"time":281714,"text":"will go to great lengths to preserve \nthis tiny piece of anatomy --"},{"time":286073,"text":"from female genital mutilation,"},{"time":288278,"text":"to virginity testing, to hymen repair surgery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292639,"text":"Faiza chose a different route:"},{"time":295645,"text":"non-vaginal sex."},{"time":298028,"text":"Only she became pregnant all the same."},{"time":300637,"text":"But Faiza didn't actually realize this,"},{"time":303377,"text":"because there's so little \nsexuality education in schools,"},{"time":307152,"text":"and so little communication in the family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311174,"text":"When her condition became hard to hide,"},{"time":313929,"text":"Faiza's mother helped her flee \nher father and brothers."},{"time":318376,"text":"This is because honor killings are a real threat"},{"time":321397,"text":"for untold numbers of women in the Arab region."},{"time":325171,"text":"And so when Faiza eventually fetched up at \na hospital in Casablanca,"},{"time":330221,"text":"the man who offered to help her,"},{"time":332898,"text":"instead tried to rape her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338350,"text":"Sadly, Faiza is not alone."},{"time":341459,"text":"In Egypt, where my research is focused,"},{"time":343245,"text":"I have seen plenty of trouble \nin and out of the citadel."},{"time":348843,"text":"There are legions of young men"},{"time":352182,"text":"who can't afford to get married,"},{"time":354289,"text":"because marriage has become \na very expensive proposition."},{"time":357713,"text":"They are expected to bear the burden\nof costs in married life,"},{"time":361272,"text":"but they can't find jobs."},{"time":363576,"text":"This is one of the major drivers \nof the recent uprisings,"},{"time":366750,"text":"and it is one of the reasons for the \nrising age of marriage"},{"time":369915,"text":"in much of the Arab region."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372946,"text":"There are career women who want to get married,"},{"time":375721,"text":"but can't find a husband,"},{"time":377319,"text":"because they defy gender expectations,"},{"time":380504,"text":"or as one young female doctor \nin Tunisia put it to me,"},{"time":384291,"text":"\"The women, they are becoming more and more open."},{"time":386998,"text":"But the man, he is still at the prehistoric stage.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":392801,"text":"And then there are men and women who \ncross the heterosexual line,"},{"time":396691,"text":"who have sex with their own sex,"},{"time":398593,"text":"or who have a different gender identity."},{"time":401602,"text":"They are on the receiving end of laws\nwhich punish their activities,"},{"time":405555,"text":"even their appearance."},{"time":407613,"text":"And they face a daily struggle with social stigma,"},{"time":411448,"text":"with family despair,"},{"time":413083,"text":"and with religious fire and brimstone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417251,"text":"Now, it's not as if it's all rosy \nin the marital bed either."},{"time":421449,"text":"Couples who are looking for greater happiness,"},{"time":423975,"text":"greater sexual happiness in their married lives,"},{"time":426614,"text":"but are at a loss of how to achieve it,"},{"time":428973,"text":"especially wives, who are afraid \nof being seen as bad women"},{"time":433495,"text":"if they show some spark in the bedroom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436699,"text":"And then there are those whose marriages"},{"time":438623,"text":"are actually a veil for prostitution."},{"time":441729,"text":"They have been sold by their families,"},{"time":443887,"text":"often to wealthy Arab tourists."},{"time":446768,"text":"This is just one face of a booming \nsex trade across the Arab region."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452369,"text":"Now raise your hand if any of \nthis is sounding familiar to you,"},{"time":456557,"text":"from your part of the world."},{"time":460527,"text":"Yeah. It's not as if the Arab world\nhas a monopoly on sexual hangups."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466537,"text":"And although we don't yet have\nan Arab Kinsey Report"},{"time":469507,"text":"to tell us exactly what's happening \ninside bedrooms across the Arab region,"},{"time":473920,"text":"It's pretty clear that \nsomething is not right."},{"time":477863,"text":"Double standards for men and women,"},{"time":480551,"text":"sex as a source of shame,"},{"time":483810,"text":"family control limiting individual choices,"},{"time":487961,"text":"and a vast gulf between appearance and reality:"},{"time":491708,"text":"what people are doing"},{"time":493294,"text":"and what they're willing to admit to,"},{"time":495639,"text":"and a general reluctance to move \nbeyond private whispers"},{"time":499615,"text":"to a serious and sustained public discussion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503703,"text":"As one doctor in Cairo summed it up for me,"},{"time":507192,"text":"\"Here, sex is the opposite of sport."},{"time":510517,"text":"Football, everybody talks about it,"},{"time":512683,"text":"but hardly anyone plays."},{"time":514653,"text":"But sex, everybody is doing it,"},{"time":516626,"text":"but nobody wants to talk about it.\"\n(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":520775,"text":"(Music) (In Arabic)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531348,"text":"SEF: I want to give you a piece of advice,"},{"time":534007,"text":"which if you follow it,\nwill make you happy in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538101,"text":"When your husband reaches out to you,"},{"time":540476,"text":"when he seizes a part of your body,"},{"time":543288,"text":"sigh deeply and look at him lustily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546654,"text":"When he penetrates you with his penis,"},{"time":549177,"text":"try to talk flirtatiously and \nmove yourself in harmony with him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554470,"text":"Hot stuff!"},{"time":555928,"text":"And it might sound that these handy hints"},{"time":557922,"text":"come from \"The Joy of Sex\" or YouPorn."},{"time":561033,"text":"But in fact, they come from\na 10th-century Arabic book"},{"time":564885,"text":"called \"The Encyclopedia of Pleasure,\""},{"time":567217,"text":"which covers sex from aphrodisiacs to zoophilia,"},{"time":571365,"text":"and everything in between."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574438,"text":"The Encyclopedia is just one \nin a long line of Arabic erotica,"},{"time":578496,"text":"much of it written by religious scholars."},{"time":581725,"text":"Going right back to the Prophet Muhammad,"},{"time":584086,"text":"there is a rich tradition in Islam"},{"time":586503,"text":"of talking frankly about sex:"},{"time":589083,"text":"not just its problems, but also its pleasures,"},{"time":592378,"text":"and not just for men, but also for women."},{"time":596953,"text":"A thousand years ago, we used to have \nwhole dictionaries of sex in Arabic."},{"time":602820,"text":"Words to cover every conceivable sexual feature,"},{"time":606973,"text":"position and preference, a body of language"},{"time":610565,"text":"that was rich enough to make up the body \nof the woman you see on this page."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617096,"text":"Today, this history is largely unknown \nin the Arab region."},{"time":620699,"text":"Even by educated people, who often\nfeel more comfortable talking about sex"},{"time":625503,"text":"in a foreign language than they do\nin their own tongue."},{"time":630481,"text":"Today's sexual landscape looks\na lot like Europe and America"},{"time":634204,"text":"on the brink of the sexual revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636937,"text":"But while the West has opened on sex,"},{"time":639985,"text":"what we found is that Arab societies appear\nto have been moving in the opposite direction."},{"time":646618,"text":"In Egypt and many of its neighbors,"},{"time":648873,"text":"this closing down is part of a wider closing"},{"time":651750,"text":"in political, social and cultural thought."},{"time":655333,"text":"And it is the product of a complex historical process,"},{"time":659389,"text":"one which has gained ground with the rise \nof Islamic conservatism"},{"time":663182,"text":"since the late 1970s."},{"time":666183,"text":"\"Just say no\" is what conservatives \naround the world"},{"time":669858,"text":"say to any challenge to the sexual status quo."},{"time":674320,"text":"In the Arab region, they brand these attempts\nas a Western conspiracy"},{"time":678606,"text":"to undermine traditional Arab\nand Islamic values."},{"time":682908,"text":"But what's really at stake here"},{"time":684907,"text":"is one of their most powerful tools of control:"},{"time":688801,"text":"sex wrapped up in religion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692958,"text":"But history shows us that \neven as recently"},{"time":696103,"text":"as our fathers' and grandfathers' day,"},{"time":699012,"text":"there have been times of greater pragmatism,"},{"time":701961,"text":"and tolerance, and a willingness\nto consider other interpretations:"},{"time":707481,"text":"be it abortion, or masturbation, or even \nthe incendiary topic of homosexuality."},{"time":714400,"text":"It is not black and white,\nas conservatives would have us believe."},{"time":719266,"text":"In these, as in so many other matters,"},{"time":722473,"text":"Islam offers us at least 50 shades of gray."},{"time":725894,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":728308,"text":"Over my travels,"},{"time":729457,"text":"I've met men and women \nacross the Arab region"},{"time":732065,"text":"who've been exploring that spectrum --"},{"time":735058,"text":"sexologists who are trying\nto help couples"},{"time":737762,"text":"find greater happiness in their marriages,"},{"time":741684,"text":"innovators who are managing to get \nsexuality education into schools,"},{"time":747366,"text":"small groups of men and women,"},{"time":749733,"text":"lesbian, gay, transgendered, transsexual,"},{"time":752449,"text":"who are reaching out to their peers"},{"time":754130,"text":"with online initiatives and real-world support."},{"time":758788,"text":"Women, and increasingly men,\nwho are starting to speak out"},{"time":762751,"text":"and push back against sexual violence"},{"time":765837,"text":"on the streets and in the home."},{"time":769393,"text":"Groups that are trying to help sex workers\nprotect themselves against HIV"},{"time":774126,"text":"and other occupational hazards,"},{"time":776993,"text":"and NGOs that are helping unwed mothers like Faiza"},{"time":780921,"text":"find a place in society, and critically,\nstay with their kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":786702,"text":"Now these efforts are small, \nthey're often underfunded,"},{"time":790113,"text":"and they face formidable opposition."},{"time":793416,"text":"But I am optimistic that, in the long run,"},{"time":796944,"text":"times are changing, and they and their ideas"},{"time":800321,"text":"will gain ground."},{"time":802250,"text":"Social change doesn't happen in the Arab region\nthrough dramatic confrontation,"},{"time":807902,"text":"beating or indeed baring of breasts,"},{"time":811289,"text":"but rather through negotiation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":813754,"text":"What we're talking here is not about a \nsexual revolution,"},{"time":817424,"text":"but a sexual evolution, \nlearning from other parts of the world,"},{"time":821898,"text":"adapting to local conditions,"},{"time":824274,"text":"forging our own path,\nnot following one blazed by another."},{"time":830161,"text":"That path, I hope, will one day lead us \nto the right to control our own bodies,"},{"time":836604,"text":"and to access the information \nand services we need"},{"time":839674,"text":"to lead satisfying and safe sexual lives."},{"time":844078,"text":"The right to express our ideas freely,"},{"time":846648,"text":"to marry whom we choose, \nto choose our own partners,"},{"time":851303,"text":"to be sexually active or not,\nto decide whether to have children and when,"},{"time":856155,"text":"all this without violence or force or discrimination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":862534,"text":"Now we are very far from this \nacross the Arab region,"},{"time":865938,"text":"and so much needs to change:"},{"time":869045,"text":"law, education, media, the economy,"},{"time":872973,"text":"the list goes on and on,"},{"time":875846,"text":"and it is the work of a generation, at least."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880164,"text":"But it begins with a journey that I myself have made,"},{"time":883326,"text":"asking hard questions of received wisdoms"},{"time":886295,"text":"in sexual life."},{"time":888103,"text":"And it is a journey which has\nonly served to strengthen my faith,"},{"time":892616,"text":"and my appreciation of local histories and cultures"},{"time":896134,"text":"by showing me possibilities \nwhere I once only saw absolutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":901929,"text":"Now given the turmoil in many\ncountries in the Arab region,"},{"time":905386,"text":"talking about sex, \nchallenging the taboos,"},{"time":908463,"text":"seeking alternatives might sound like\nsomething of a luxury."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913799,"text":"But at this critical moment in history,"},{"time":916591,"text":"if we do not anchor freedom and justice,"},{"time":920969,"text":"dignity and equality,"},{"time":922601,"text":"privacy and autonomy in our personal lives,\nin our sexual lives,"},{"time":927843,"text":"we will find it very hard to achieve in public life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932144,"text":"The political and the sexual are intimate bedfellows,\nand that is true for us all."},{"time":938899,"text":"no matter where we live and love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":942310,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":943826,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}